title: Alex & Sierra
description:
Alex & Sierra 

She is Gorgeous! seriously beautiful and they were great together. I think later in the show we saw just how young they both are. I do not know how I would have handled the pressure of a talent competition like that at the ripe old age of 22! They have amazing voices separately, I hope they can bring their talent together the way that fate has obviously brought their hearts together!

Enjoy...
